# Keep the Docker build context small. The image build (deploy/Containerfile) does a
# fresh `yarn install` + `yarn build`, so none of the excluded items are needed.
#
# NOTE: the frappe-ui submodule SOURCE is intentionally INCLUDED now — the prod build
# uses it (see frontend/vite.config.js) so submodule customizations ship to production.
# We only skip its bulky, regenerated parts (node_modules, docs, .git).
.git
**/.git
.gitmodules
**/node_modules
frappe-ui/docs
env/
sites/
logs/
graphify-out/
**/__pycache__/
*.pyc
*.pyo
.DS_Store
# build artifacts (regenerated inside the image)
crm/public/frontend/
crm/www/crm.html
